data.description: Experience country living at its finest in this 3 bed/3 bath home situated on 8.1 acres. The home also encompasses a bonus/office room, sunroom, and a walkout basement with a storm shelter, complete with a 2-car attached garage and a 2-car detached garage with 2 open bays. There's ample space for vehicles and hobbies. Enjoy the covered front porch and expansive back deck overlooking a large pond. Situated along the Mulberry River, the property has two access points—one with a private beach that is breathtaking. This stunning property includes a small creek running through the front yard, a long asphalt driveway, and a quaint log building at the back. Don't miss out!
